工具篇

1.google pagespeed insights (网站综合分析工具)
https://developers.google.com/speed/pagespeed/insights/

在chrome浏览器上安装插件
chrome://extensions/ -- "获取更多扩展程序" -- "查找pagespeed insights"

2.gimp(linux下的photoshop)

3.google的web优化建议
优化css发送过程
https://developers.google.com/speed/docs/insights/OptimizeCSSDelivery

优化图片
https://developers.google.com/speed/docs/insights/OptimizeImages

使用浏览器缓存
https://developers.google.com/speed/docs/insights/LeverageBrowserCaching

启用压缩功能
https://developers.google.com/speed/docs/insights/EnableCompression

缩减首屏内容的大小
https://developers.google.com/speed/docs/insights/PrioritizeVisibleContent

缩减资源(HTML、CSS和JavaScript)大小
https://developers.google.com/speed/docs/insights/MinifyResources

改善服务器响应时间
https://developers.google.com/speed/docs/insights/Server

避免网页目标重定向
https://developers.google.com/speed/docs/insights/AvoidRedirects

移除阻止呈现的JavaScript
https://developers.google.com/speed/docs/insights/BlockingJS

更多的优化实践
https://developers.google.com/speed/articles/compressing-javascript?hl=zh-CN
https://gtmetrix.com/avoid-charset-in-meta-tag.html

